{"tid":2289790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"FB刪除針對賀錦麗內容","createTime":"2020-11-17T13:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T14:48:32.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0289432a6ed1e0f8777786ee02518309436924fb","tid":2289790,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T13:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/82c6047bba7673dac1ea9d7dfc06cdf9/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201117/_2020111716492089568.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F82c6047bba7673dac1ea9d7dfc06cdf9%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201117%2F_2020111716492089568.jpg&h=06c671f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n社交網站 Facebook 周一採取行動，刪除了一連串含有種族主義及厭惡女性、針對美國副總統當選人賀錦麗的內容和帖文。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook 發表聲明稱，接到英國廣播公司（BBC）通知，知道有三個群組經常利用 Facebook 平台發佈此類訊息和內容，決定採取行動。該公司重申，在 Facebook 平台上出現的仇恨訊息和內容，有90%在被舉報或被標籤之前，已經被刪除，但也有些有問題的內容或訊息漏網。<br />\n<br />\n其中一個媒體監察組織指出，那些有問題的帖文和內容，涉嫌散播種族主義、厭惡或敵視女性的訊息。不過，Facebook 表示，今次行動只是刪除違規的網頁和內容，並沒有封殺發佈那些訊息和內容的組織或群組。<br />\n<br />\n一些有問題的內容，指賀錦麗不是美國公民，因為她的母親來自印度，而她的父親是來自牙買加，因此質疑她出任美國副總統的資格。其中一段帖文說，應該把賀錦麗驅逐出境，遣回印度。有些網民則發揮惡搞本色，嘲笑賀錦麗的名字。這令人聯想到前總統奧巴馬當年上任後，那時仍是商人的特朗普也指他不是在美國出生，質疑他無資格出任美國總統。<br />\n<br />\n美國本月初結束大選後，網上充斥大量失實資訊，甚至有人鼓吹暴力。上周，總統當選人拜登的助手批評 Facebook 處理陰謀論的手法。拜登的副新聞秘書拉索說：「這關乎到我們的民主。我們需要尋找答案。」<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline .com/news/realtime/wo/1926232</code></pre>"},{"pid":"fbeb1eb05775d0b068111b3310544655052e0da8","tid":2289790,"uid":286897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T13:28:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85bfd35911b2630bfdfedd99c01f3e30d406d978","tid":2289790,"uid":65201,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T13:31:09.000Z","msg":"刪得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班舊時代既父權惡魔想打壓我地新時代女性既掘起，ban撚埋佢地ip就啱"},{"pid":"1a088e876e5ba703c3d0b03e04e2b2530b817266","tid":2289790,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T13:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/133012_aa230b2a437a71187244bcebe592ed89.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F133012_aa230b2a437a71187244bcebe592ed89.png&h=02054dfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69796cebeea6e6875b08ee9ad58886e53899ac87","tid":2289790,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T13:59:12.000Z","msg":"Fuck political correctness"},{"pid":"d03bd754c1f99979a993068e94594585b665119d","tid":2289790,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:02:29.000Z","msg":"Fucking black cunt<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218fd54cd4fbc3e27418c8ecc198ee01872ce7ac","tid":2289790,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:04:28.000Z","msg":"社會主義好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54179271ab585bc6bce53c3d952806235f274da1","tid":2289790,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f98ec2acb39ba0abcc20f942a97ab1361c2fa5","tid":2289790,"uid":118120,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:06:07.000Z","msg":"點鬧 Trump 係 Racist 都冇問題<br />\n民主黨就一句都唔鬧得"},{"pid":"9fb617abdccd4ae14bb01382e6bc8174e0272189","